- Plan for your day, using your calender
- prioritize your works for that day
- should have natural lights in room
    - since it supports good health, due to its direct effect on mood and mental alertness
    - its one of the best freely available motivator
- should have less noise
- good temperature, should not have temperature distract you
- quality chair, table, extra monitors
- make your work space personal
- respect your work time, work as if as your real time work going time.
- avoid distraction, work as if you're working from your workplace
